text: That white haired boy...!!! So rude!
If you're looking for someone to play foolish games with, go find Ciel!
Oho, don't tell me that you've fallen for me now that you've seen how beautiful I am?
Ciel is very, very special indeed! ....What? Don't look at me like that, Ciel!
Stop treating me like a child!
Hmph!
Hmph.. I can handle myself perfectly well on my own!
Ohoho, Ciel's better than any other butler there is, I can assure you!
Watch your tone!
How dare you speak to me like that?!
I don't want to lose someone important to me!
...I want cake...
Me? Too old to enjoy sweets? Aren't you a little too young to be so boring?
Uuuu.... Don't make fun of my cooking!! Just because I only know how to make sweets well...
How is that elf lady always able to stay composed? ..Well, except for when it comes to the children. I don't blame her for that, though.
Hm.... nw_enbot, are you making dinner tonight, or is Ciel?
nw_enbot, I think those three children are up to no good again.. Could you hurry up and put leashes on them?
Ughh-! There's blood all over the place! cra_enbot, quit making messes like this!
..Elesis actually gave me something. Ah, these ribbons... She has good taste. I should thank her again later.
asura_enbot, don't rush things. ...I'm certain that we can save your brother.
asura_enbot, are you sure that you can trust Eun?
..I'm starting to think there's more to Ara than it seems.
diabolic_enbot, where did you and Elesis run off to now?! At least tell me about it!
Add's fixation on wanting to go back in time... I understand it.
diabolic_enbot... Is there any way I could be of help to you?
cra_enbot, you haven't been skipping out on meals again, have you? Ciel's food is good!! Amazing! You absolutely can't miss it.. okay?
cra_enbot... Are you alright? Don't overwork yourself. It'd be a nuisance if you fainted in the middle of battle.
..I wish Ciel didn't beat himself up over something like losing. I'm just as much to blame, if not even more so.
I might not be a queen, but I'm still above you in rank. Don't forget that.
I'm going to make them pay..
..I might demand respect, but I won't be cruel.
Eh? cem_enbot, doesn't it ever bother you, the way Add looks at you? That's odd..
cem_enbot, Oberon is acting strange towards me. What is this air of fear around him, oho?
Huh? Do I need Ciel to be the one to brush my hair and cook for me? Well, no, but... Don't question me!
Despite how blunt Elsword is, he seems to have a hard time being honest when it comes to Elesis. It's alright for him to say that he missed her.. What a child.
Surprised to see me like this? I told you, didn't I? Now I'll show you the full extent of my power!
...I must admit, it feels nice to have the tables turn. I've seen the way Aisha looks at my figure!
Who's Kyubey? What's this about contracts? Don't be stupid.
Raven is powerful, but lacking in charisma. The way he looks at Rena makes his feelings clear! ..Hm, but I suppose I don't dislike that about him.
Ciel, handle this for me.
Did those traitors give out my whole wardrobe?? Why does everyone in Lanox have such similar clothes to me?
I refuse to lose to the likes of you..!
It appears that Eve and I are more alike than we thought- but why has she started talking to me more often since I went back to this form?
Chung is somehow a likable kid, if a little stiff compared to his friends. I don't doubt that he'd make a fine ruler someday.
...I'd do anything to protect him.
Ara is a kind girl and deserves respect for her conviction. But, I wonder why she clings to that brother so much.. It'd be much easier to just do away with him.
Elesis.. What do I have to do to earn her trust..? But I understand her dislike of me.
